      "date": "2011-05-09 19:37:00.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\n(1 inline comment)\n\nThere is one build failure (i686/el6), which is related to a missing configuration file for that kernel.  Please rebase your branch to include git change hash dc9008c033d13a156989fd49e47a3a30a79cb5ac, make the minor \"offset\" vs \"obd\" reordering and resubmit the patch.\n\nThe patch itself is fine, which is why I'm giving it +1 in spite of the unrelated build failure.   Sorry for the inconvenience.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "9ea6b02263d747c858051b9842594ee1c33fe974",
