      },
      "date": "2011-05-19 15:55:23.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 7:\n\nOk, So this version (Patch Set 7) should not have any dependencies and is rebased onto what was the HEAD of master as of a few minutes ago. I do not plan to update this patch with any new versions, thus my hope is it can be landed as is.\n\nI hope this clears up any confusion and makes the review process more straight forward.",
